txt.en: Hobgoblin hunters can be found near Ibdêkh-buzru, the Thing-fold.\n\nYou should defeat hobgoblin hunters.
'Nice work, [placeholder]. I trust in the runes that surround the Thing-fold, but still... we should keep those hobgoblins as far from here as we can!'
Kyrstig can be found near Ibdêkh-buzru, the Thing-fold.\n\nYou should talk to Kyrstig.

'While you're here, I have another hobgoblin-related report for you. Can you believe it?'

Kyrstig laughs.

'I've seen a few of them sneaking around near the Thing-fold, among the trees and shrubs. Luckily, the old runes seem to remain in effect, and the hobgoblins are reluctant to set foot among the statues. Still, I worry that in time they may be able to overcome that reluctance. I think their hunters are seeking game to feed their forces, but what if their hunt turns up something else? Let's do something about those hunters before they interfere with our plans!'
Kyrstig has noticed some hobgoblins lurking near Ibdêkh-buzru, the Thing-fold.
